> WHEELIE heaved a sigh of relief then over as GRIMLOCK stopped his charge,
> his first comment thrown out to the DINOBOT FIRETROOPER, "No offense SLAG,
> but you sill always MAD."
>
> WHEELIE went to relax then, forcibly looking up and locking his optics upon
> GRIMLOCK, "Me WHEELIE know something is wrong.  Wonders if GRIMLOCk knows
> what is going on?"
>
> Glancing at the other DINOBOTS now, to see if they could offer any
> explanations.

<NEW>

"Me Grimlock not know what is going on!' He said angrily, far more
angry that was he normally was, his optics still flickering between
his normal sanity levels and what it was that was affecting him.

SLAG looked at WHEELIE, "Slag always wants to crush and destroy!"

Whatever it was that was affecting them was not over, it was just
being held at bay by the DINOBOT's formidable stubbornness.

"Me Grimlock say Wheelie needs to go!" GRIMLOCK said, his optics
beginning to darken.

"No Grimlock you can fight it." This voice was SWOOP'S as he
transformed and landed.

GRIMLOCK looked at SWOOP the anger rising, "No! Me Grimlock no listen
to you! Swoop traitor!"

The other DINOBOTS nodded their heads as their optics flickered again.
What ever it was they were fighting internally, the DINOBOT'S resolve
was beginning to weaken or perhaps their anger against SWOOP was being
used against them.

(TAG)

- Preston
